<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Arch2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Arch,</orth> adj. wicked, arrant: <cit><quote>the most a. act of piteous massacre,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.3.2" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 3, 2</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>that a. heretic,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 3.1.192" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 1, 192</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>an heretic, an a. one,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.102" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 102</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a most a. heretic,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 5.1.45" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 45</bibl></cit> (cf. <emph>arch-enemy, arch-mock, arch-villain).</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>